'''Christopher Odhiambo Okinda''' (yavutse 15 Ukuboza 1980), ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Kenya]] . <ref>https://www.filmportal.de/en/person/christopher-okinda_ea383d3344434d52ba0569cd039ce5d7</ref> <ref>https://www.wunschliste.de/person/christopher-okinda</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime ''[[The Constant Gardener (film)|The Constant Gardener]]'' na ''The White Massai'' . <ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2bd291f5a</ref> Usibye gukina, ni n'umuyobozi wa firime, producer, umwanditsi hamwe n'umunyamakuru wa Radio. <ref name=":0">https://rankly.com/item/christopher-odhiambo-okinda</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 15 Ukuboza 1980 i Mombasa, muri Kenya kuri Elizabeth Apiyo Aruwa na Alois Okinda. Se yari afite abagore benshi, bityo yarezwe na nyina babanaga. Yabanje kwiga mu ishuri ribanza rya Aga Khan (Parklands, Kenya) hanyuma Bikira Mariya w'Ishuri ribanza ryimbabazi. Nyuma, yimukiye muri St Peter's Mumias Boys primaire mu 1994 arangije ishuri rya St Mary (muri Yala) mu 1996. <ref name=":0" />

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2005, yatangiye gukina filime muri firime ishimishije ''[[The Constant Gardener (film)|The Constant Gardener]]'' iyobowe na Fernando Meirelles . Okinda yagize uruhare ruto rwo gushyigikira nka 'Muganga' muri film. <ref>https://catalog.afi.com/Film/63355-THE-CONSTANTGARDENER?sid=2a2f0467-a130-4b8c-a9a1-28425bf6e886&sr=9.742409&cp=1&pos=0</ref> Iyi filime yakiriwe neza kandi yerekanwa mu birori byinshi bya firime. <ref>http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/constant_gardener</ref>

Hamwe nitsinzi yumukobwa we wambere yakinnye, yahise atoranywa muri ''White Massai'' 2005. Hagati aho, yashinze firime yikinamico 'Something Productions'. Binyuze muri sosiyete, yakinnye amakinamico mu rurimi kavukire rwa nyina Dholuo. Usibye gukina, kuri ubu akora nka radio yerekana igitondo akaba numuyobozi uhanga 'Hot 96 FM' muri Kenya. <ref name=":0" />

